## Key Fields for Trading Logic:

- **`contracts`**: Position size (always positive value)
- **`percentage`**: Unrealized P&L percentage 
- **`side`**: "long" or "short"
- **`entryPrice`**: Entry price of the position
- **`markPrice`**: Current market price
- **`unrealizedPnl`**: Unrealized profit/loss in USDT
